        "Setup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "setup()里按顺序是：Serial.begin(9600)串口初始化，然后是红外接收初始化IrReceiver.begin(recvPin)，接着设置引脚模式——recvPin和echoPin是输入，trigPin还有12、13号是输出，再初始化两个电机MR.begin()和ML.begin()，最后舵机srv.attach(8)并复位到0度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "A2",
        "A3",
        "A4",
        "A5",
        "A6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我记下了六个初始化节点，从A1到A6顺序连接。那loop循环里先做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loop",
